    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2026-06-03</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2026-06-05T14:17:14Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution provides for the House of Representatives to consider&nbsp;on the same day without a two-thirds vote&nbsp;any resolution reported by the Committee on Rules through the legislative day of June 5, 2026, relating to a measure providing for reconciliation pursuant to title II of S.Con.Res.33. Specifically, the resolution waives a House Rule requiring a two-thirds vote to consider a report from the Committee on Rules on the same day it is presented to the House.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Waiving a requirement of clause 6(a) of rule XIII with respect to consideration of certain resolutions reported from the Committee on Rules.</title>
